org.theospi.portfolio.wizard.tool

Interface DecoratedListInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DecoratedCategory, DecoratedCategoryChild, DecoratedWizard, DecoratedWizardPage

    public interface DecoratedListInterface
    This class is for defining the methods used to display the pages and categories We also want to show the wizard itself in the case of the hierachical wizard
    Author:
    andersjb
